Description:
Leap into the air and throw a hatchet that deals &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;{[DamageTable.Hatchet_Damage_InfectedThrow.DmgCoef * 100]}%&lt;/font&gt; &lt;img src="lyshineui/images/icons/tooltip/icon_tooltip_slash_opaque" xPadding="4" scale="1.7" yOffset="4"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;weapon damage.
This attack inflicts &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;{[Type_StatusEffectData.Hatchet_Infected_Disease.HealMod * -100]}% disease&lt;/font&gt; and &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;{[Type_StatusEffectData.Hatchet_Infected_Weaken.DMGStandard * -100]}% weaken&lt;/font&gt; to your target for &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;{[Type_StatusEffectData.Hatchet_Infected_Disease.BaseDuration]}s&lt;/font&gt;.&lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_Regular_Italic.font" color="#828282"&gt;

(Disease reduces target's incoming healing efficiency and outgoing healing efficiency by half the incoming value.)
(Weaken reduces target's outgoing damage.)&lt;/font&gt;
